Prompt: How can I filter data by age group?
Response: To filter data by age groups, click on the fingerprint icon located at the top right-hand side of the page. From there, you can adjust the age groups.
Follow-Up Prompt: Would you like help selecting a specific age range?
Follow-Up Response: You can select specific ranges such as 0-5, 6-12, 13-18, etc. Do you have a particular range in mind?
